and throw the shark back to die.

794
00:50:02,479 --> 00:50:04,432
All for a bowl of soup.

795
00:50:04,822 --> 00:50:07,125
Looks like the meg
evened the score.

796
00:50:11,687 --> 00:50:14,002
One fish did all this?

797
